creator: SwishLive
descriptionHtml:
With Swish Live, broadcast your sports events, like on TV, from your smartphone!

Manage yourself the scoreboard in real time. The app will embed in your live: names of teams, colors of jerseys, remaining time and scoreboard depending on the sport you practice.

You can now stream all your matches directly to your Facebook or Youtube page!

Swish Live creates a new media spot for your sponsors! Add their logos directly overlay on the live. This will allow you to multiply your audience and generate easily a new revenue stream.


Football, Futsal, Volley Ball, Beach Volleyball, Tennis, Table Tennis, Rugby, Handball, Basketball and Badminton are available to stream on the app.

Broadcast your events like on TV!

# The key features:

• Inlay of an editable scorecard in real time:
• The title of the match (Championship Day, Cup Final, ...)
• The names of the teams
• The color of the jerseys of each team
• The score in real time (Game, set, goals, test, ...)
• Live modifiable time
• For basketball, bring up the quarter-time your team is playing
• Inlay of your sponsor's logo


Real-time comments: Make your match live to all your fans


Swish Live is a very easy application to set up. Set up your match easily in a matter of minutes and go live on your club page very quickly.

# Support:

Write us your comments, suggestions or requests. We will respond as soon as possible. We respond daily to your requests, with the aim of continuously improving our application: contact@swishlive.com
